description:
Welcome to a tech-filled dystopian future. DystoPunks is a utility-focused cyberpunk-themed NFT project that allows holders to generate a utility-governance token called $CREDS and use it in the Dystolab.

Voxel Avatars: [DystoPunks VX](https://opensea.io/collection/dystopunks-vx) | [Dystolab Crates](https://opensea.io/collection/dystolab-crates)

Punks of the Metaverse | By: [Dekadente](https://twitter.com/0xDekadente)

[Website](https://dystopunks.net/) | [Discord](https://discord.gg/DystoPunks) | [Medium](https://dystopunks.medium.com/) | [Twitter](https://twitter.com/DystoPunks)
